<div class="c230_117">
<div id="v230.117.1"><span class="H1984 s">O praise</span><span class="H3068 s"> the LORD</span><span class="H1471 s">, all ye nations</span><span class="H7623 s">: praise</span><span class="H523 s"> him, all ye people</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.117.2"><span class="H2617 s">For his merciful</span><span class="H2617 s"> kindness</span><span class="H1396 s"> is great</span><span class="H571 s"> toward us: and the truth</span><span class="H3068 s"> of the LORD</span><span class="H5769 s"> <i>endureth</i> for ever</span><span class="H1984 s">. Praise</span><span class="H3050 s"> ye the LORD</span>.</div></div>
